I'm not gonna lie.

20:50.333 --> 20:52.375
Fun birthday.

20:55.625 --> 20:59.250
Hey! Never thought I'd see
you dirty bastards again.

20:59.291 --> 21:01.583
Ah! I feel great,
cleaned out.

21:01.625 --> 21:05.208
All right, who wants 'em next?
No one?

21:05.250 --> 21:07.750
Okay, you heard them.
Round two, boys.

21:07.792 --> 21:10.458
And make sure this time
that you really--

21:10.500 --> 21:12.625
Oh. Oh, you know
what you're doing.

